Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit digital cityscape at night where glowing speech bubbles float upward from buildings like digital lanterns, each bubble containing abstract geometric patterns instead of words. In the foreground, a translucent holographic form dynamically assembles itself piece by piece from floating code fragments and pixel streams. The scene features deep purple and electric blue tones with hot pink accent lighting. Circuit board patterns are embedded in the wet pavement reflecting the neon glow. A protective dome of interlocking hexagonal shields surrounds one central speech bubble, suggesting security and filtering. Moths with binary-pattern wings swarm around the brightest neon signs but are deflected away from the shielded areas. The atmosphere is moody and technological, with rain streaking through laser grid lines in the sky.
